code: @Override public int hashCode() {     return Objects.hash(total, min, max, avg). }

@Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     if (this == obj) {         return true.     }     if (obj == null || getClass() != obj.getClass()) {         return false.     }     SimpleStats other = (SimpleStats) obj.     return Objects.equals(total, other.total) && Objects.equals(min, other.min) && Objects.equals(avg, other.avg) && Objects.equals(max, other.max). }

@Override public XContentBuilder toXContent(XContentBuilder builder, Params params) throws IOException {     builder.startObject().     builder.field(MIN.getPreferredName(), min).     builder.field(MAX.getPreferredName(), max).     builder.field(AVG.getPreferredName(), avg).     builder.field(TOTAL.getPreferredName(), total).     builder.endObject().     return builder. }
